   <abstract>The data in this report were collected from local child care resource and referral agencies (CCR&amp;R) through a survey sent to agencies in each state to identify data on child care costs in an urban area, in a rural area, and/or statewide. Average family income is compared to the cost of child care in each state and in each area, and data collected is compared across the states.</abstract>
